@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_waeqmz(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = ((wp.exp(v0 + 0.95) / (tmp + 0.34 * tmp + 0.27)) / v2)
    v1 = ((v2 + 0.97) / wp.abs(wp.cos(v0 + 0.37)))
    tmp = wp.cos(v2)
    tmp = tmp
    tmp = wp.abs(tmp)
    tmp = 0.36
    tmp = wp.exp(wp.cos(tmp))
    v2 = wp.exp((0.78 + v1))
    data[tid] = v0
